flowchart TD
    A[User / External System] --> B[Interface Layer]
    B --> C[Command Layer]
    C --> D[Application Layer]
    D --> E[Module Layer]
    E --> F[Kernel Layer]
    F --> G[Data Layer]
    G --> H{Automation Required?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Automation Layer]
    I --> J{External Integration?}
    H -- No --> K[Response]
    J -- Yes --> L[Integration Layer]
    J -- No --> K
    L --> K
    K --> D
    D --> C
    C --> B
    B --> M[User Response]
